<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Konfirmasi Pemesanan - Hotel De Luna</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@600&family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root {
      --primary-color: #2c2c2c;
      --accent-color: #d4a373;
      --bg-color: #fcf8f1;
      --white: #ffffff;
      --status-bg: #fff4e6;
      --status-text: #d4a373;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
      background-color: var(--bg-color);
      color: var(--primary-color);
      margin: 0;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      min-height: 100vh;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .confirmation-card {
      background: var(--white);
      max-width: 500px;
      width: 100%;
      padding: 50px 40px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      text-align: center;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    /* Aksen garis emas di atas */
    .confirmation-card::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      height: 6px;
      background: var(--accent-color);
    }

    .icon-success {
      font-size: 3rem;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      display: block;
    }

    h2 {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: 2rem;
      margin: 0 0 10px 0;
    }

    .subtitle {
      color: #888;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    .detail-box {
      background: #fafafa;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 25px;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      text-align: left;
      border: 1px solid #eee;
    }

    .detail-item {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .detail-item:last-child {
      margin-bottom: 0;
      padding-top: 12px;
      border-top: 1px dashed #ddd;
    }

    .label {
      color: #777;
    }

    .value {
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .status-badge {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 6px 16px;
      background: var(--status-bg);
      color: var(--status-text);
      border-radius: 50px;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }

    .btn-home {
      display: block;
      background: var(--primary-color);
      color: var(--white);
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-weight: 500;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }

    .btn-home:hover {
      background: #000;
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }

    @media (max-width: 480px) {
      .confirmation-card {
        padding: 30px 20px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="confirmation-card">
    <span class="icon-success">🛎️</span>
    <h2>Pemesanan Berhasil</h2>
    <p class="subtitle">Terima kasih telah memilih Hotel De Luna. Silakan selesaikan pembayaran Anda.</p>

    <div class="detail-box">
      <div class="detail-item">
        <span class="label">ID Booking</span>
        <span class="value">#<%= booking.id %></span>
      </div>
      <div class="detail-item">
        <span class="label">Check-in</span>
        <span class="value"><%= booking.checkin.toISOString().split('T')[0] %></span>
      </div>
      <div class="detail-item">
        <span class="label">Check-out</span>
        <span class="value"><%= booking.checkout.toISOString().split('T')[0] %></span>
      </div>
      <div class="detail-item">
        <span class="label">Status</span>
        <span class="status-badge">Menunggu Pembayaran</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <a href="/booking/homepage" class="btn-home">Kembali ke Homepage</a>
  </div>

</body>
</html>